item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Bandwidth_GraphInputs
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Bandwidth_GraphInputs Datatype Description SoftLayer_Container_Bandwidth_GraphInputs models a single inbound object for a given bandwidth graph. Local endDate This is a unix timestamp that represents the stop date/time for a graph. Type: dateTime networkInterfaceId The front-end or back-end network uplink interface associated with this server. Type: integer pod * Type: integer serverName This is a human readable name for the server or rack being graphed.
